## Purpose

This hook is useful for when you would want to lock the scroll
behavior depending on a boolean value. For example, if you have a
semi-transparent navigation menu, you probably wouldn't want the user
to be able to scroll as the content behind the navigation menu would scroll
and that wouldn't provide the best user experience.

